core.name: Addicted To Love Blush Pink Maxi Dress
core.description: Some are addicted to illicit substances. Others, to attention. But you, like so many women before you, have a much more intoxicating, and far more difficult addiction to grapple with; you’re addicted to love, and the only cure is being wooed and pursued like the precious prize you are. And like the knights errant, donning their armor as they prepare to win your heart, your armor is your wardrobe, and this dress far more essential than chain mail (without all the chafing). This gorgeous dress is beyond what any fairy godmother could provide because a) it won't turn into produce at any time of day or night and b) it doesn't come with any strings attached. core.name: At Every Turn Pink Print Open Shoulder Dress
core.description: Doesn't it seem like there is something new and exciting At Every Turn? Do you ever feel like in this digital age of a thousand flashing images and air-brushed everything, that natural beauty can't compete with all of those images in those high fashion magazines that show unrealistic expectations of what a woman looks like? Here's the deal: there's nothing more beautiful in this world than imperfection, and no one is holding you to those expectations but you. Yes, I said it. You're the only one who thinks you're supposed to look like a runway model. Most men are merely happy to see you smile, they don't actually read fashion magazines (ask one of them if you don't believe me). Other women are too busy feeling insecure about themselves most of the time to worry about you or what you look like. What you -should- focus on, is this moment right now. Look at yourself, in this moment, and see how lovely you look in this Open Shoulder Dress. It's stunning, and you look every bit outside the

core.name: Call The Shots Beige Jacket
core.description: No matter how many women are sitting at the table, when someone from outside the group walks up, it takes approximately five seconds to determine who among the ranks has been designated as the one to Call The Shots. How is one chosen? That's a trade secret because it differs from one group to another, but it's instinctual for others to understand the outcome. We *can* tell you, however, that it does involve clothing and the ritual of dressing. Yes, some say fashion is archaic, but since the dawn of time, mankind has used clothing as part of ceremonial rites. Why is fashion as a concept dismissed just because our understanding of it is any different? How will our ancestors 500 years in the future see us today? Yeah, that's what I thought. And just like this power jacket, what you wear says a lot about you and what place you hold in the groups you are consciously and subconsciously a part of in society. Plus, this jacket looks awesome, no matter how strong it makes you look, and that's

core.name: Casual Introduction Light Denim Ankle-Strap Sandals
core.description: It was a Casual Introduction. My friend owned a pair of these killer Light Denim Ankle Strap Sandals, and she happened to show them to me, asked if I wanted to try them on. Suddenly it was love at first sight. I couldn't think of anything else. I came home and opened my closet, glanced at my rows of shoes and wanted to cry. Something was missing. After sulking around the house all weekend, I finally realized, it was the shoes. So I called up my BFF and asked her where she got them; low and behold ... RDB. So here they are!! My heart has been found! Sandals feature a single toe strap, adjustable ankle strap and a heel cup that measures 3\". • Non-Skid Sole • Vegan friendly, man made materials • Imported
core.caption: Captions!

core.name: Casual Life Medium Wash Distressed Denim Jacket
core.description: Dear Denim Jacket, thanks for hanging in there all this time--you're my happy place on days when vintage cool is precisely what I'm going for. Your distressed exterior reminds me that the years are to be appreciated, not warded off; lingered in, not rushed through; thoroughly enjoyed, not dreaded. So thank you my friend. Here's to all the good times! Distressed button up denim jacket features four functional pockets with button cuffs. Model is wearing a small. • 99% Cotton 1% Spandex • Machine Wash Cold • Unlined • Imported
core.caption: Captions!

core.name: Catch The Light Purple Pendant Earrings
core.description: You know how some jewelry just catches the light so perfectly that it positively dazzles you whenever you stare at it? Well, our team of experts have outdone themselves. They’ve literally caught light, much like a firefly, and trapped it in a jar. Then, through a complicated process involving a lot of pseudo-physics, they compress those glistening rays into finely cut crystal, which we’ve made into earrings just for you. See the sparkles for yourself, and you’ll know that, while we might be a little full of it, there’s no denying how well they Watch the Light. Crystal Earrings feature drop crystal with rhinestone details. **No Pseudo-physics were injured in the making of these earrings ... that we're aware of.
core.caption: Captions!
